{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ea55c3707a","title":"和钱学森等的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"26e8aa5ac5","index":0,"year":1964,"month":2,"day":6,"articleId":"ea55c3707a"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"4d5b78c420","name":"钱学森","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji46","name":"毛泽东全集第46卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/46-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji46":{"comments":[{"id":"6cf4e1c465","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"ea55c3707a","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东和著名科学家钱学森、李四光、兰可杭等谈话的一部分。"}],"contents":[{"id":"d9cc1593e2","type":"title","text":"和钱学森等的谈话”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"ea55c3707a"},{"id":"6cf4e1c465","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东（以下简称毛）：我们搞原子弹也有成绩呀！","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"ea55c3707a"},{"id":"5ad2c24873","type":"paragraph","text":"钱学森（以下简称钱）：我有所闻。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"ea55c3707a"},{"id":"f66b1e5acf","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：怕是不止有所闻吧","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"ea55c3707a"},{"id":"3c2db8f973","type":"paragraph","text":"钱：对原子弹确实只是有所闻，我是研究运载工具的。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"ea55c3707a"},{"id":"e45bed6708","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：是的。你们搞了个一千公里的，将来再搞个两干公里的，也就差不多了。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"ea55c3707a"},{"id":"467709a16d","type":"paragraph","text":"钱：美帝在东南亚新月形包围圈上的有些基地，有两千八百公里的距离。","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"ea55c3707a"},{"id":"e867004784","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：可以到夏威夷","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"ea55c3707a"},{"id":"14672a2c66","type":"paragraph","text":"钱：夏威夷更远了，不止四千公里。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"ea55c3707a"},{"id":"9ca86cbb94","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：总要搞防御。搞山洞，钻进地下去就不怕它了。","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"ea55c3707a"},{"id":"b3c587f1d6","type":"paragraph","text":"钱：我们正在遵照主席的指示，先组织一个小型的科学技术人员的小组，准备研究一下防弹道式导弹的方法、技术途径。看来第三个五年计划中由于技术条件不够，还不能开展设计工作。","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"ea55c3707a"},{"id":"93e7f64be4","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：有矛必有盾。搞少数人，专门研究这个问题。五年不行，十年；十年不行，十五年，总要搞出来的。","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"ea55c3707a"}],"page":{"id":"ac1ba2a823","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"ea55c3707a","start":257,"end":257}}}},"__N_SSG":true}